message.body: Good morning Missy. How are you doing?
Sorry - I forgot to reply to this. I'm good - I had to cancel my appt bc I have my period so it'll be next week at Scott's dad's clinic next week. Cara is here to see the show tonight :)

Yea, some frustration... But mostly well
